Don't get me wrong.  I loved SS as a kid.  It, and Mr. Rogers were the best thing in childrens television out there.  I would feel safer letting them watch those shows than anything else on TV, because they truly care about children.  But I truly feel that this is treading on parental rights too much.  <br>
